							運用「傷寒論」方的臨床思路
							
							



並列篇名
Clinical Approaches in Applying Formulas of the ＂Shang Han Lun＂


作者
劉亞光


中文摘要
傷寒論的方劑，藥簡效宏，應用廣泛。以其臨床運用的思想，歸納成：典型證候，重複驗證男；方證不全，著眼主證…等十二項。作為使用傷寒論方的參考。


英文摘要
The herbal drugs in the formulas of ”Shang Han Lun” are simple but effective and widely accepted in clinical application. The following main points for the clinical application of these formulas are: 1. For the treatment of symptoms which already stated. 2. For the treatment of main symptom. 3. For the treatment of origin or cause of the diseases. 4. Compared the symptoms appeared in patient between what stated in ”Shang Han Lun”, to make a diagnosis by the patient’s response to the herbal drugs. 5. For the treatment of various symptom caused by same etiological factor. To broaden the clinical application by really understanding the mechanism of physiological function. 6. Treatment of contradictory symptoms by the same formulas. 7. Treatment of complex symptoms by using different formulas concurrently, applying modern medical knowledge and scientific experimental results.


起訖頁
163-167


關鍵詞
傷寒論、經方、Shang Han Lun、Classical formulas


刊名
中醫藥雜誌　　


